title: KWAT
text: KWAT (950 <a href="AM%20broadcasting">AM</a>) is a <a href="radio%20station">radio station</a> broadcasting a <a href="news/talk">news/talk</a> format serving the <a href="Watertown%2C%20South%20Dakota">Watertown, South Dakota</a> area. The station is owned and operated by <a href="Alpha%20Media">Alpha Media</a> after it purchased the stations of Digity, LLC.
